product.long-description-lt: Product Description Material: Plastic + Bamboo Size: 19.5 * 19.5 * 25 cm (Bathroom) Color: White Quantity: 1 set Package Contents: 1 * Household Bathroom 1. Eco-friendly material Bathroom accessories set made of natural bamboo finish and eco-friendly polypropylene plastic, easy to choose, easy to clean, easy to clean which ensures their long service life and durability 2. Enjoy life with the soft color and simply modern design of the wooden bathroom accessories set, give your bathroom an elegant touch and easily create a warm atmosphere of almost a 5-star hotel with this bamboo accessory set 3. The set includes a soap dispenser, toothbrush holder, toothbrush holder, Brush cup, bathroom sink and brush holder. Modern bathroom set is perfect for more convenient access to cleaning products and not cluttering the dressing table 4. Multifunctional Perfect size and beautiful style wooden bathroom accessories with bamboo finish are suitable for the master, family or guest bathroom. They can also be elegant bathroom decoration accessories in hotels, resorts or cottages
